\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid16740468 W  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid2175332\charrsid12147403 Well no, you would meet them at the dancing class. Places l
ike that. I can't think of any - and - and friends houses, I can't think of anywhere else.
