\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid16740468 W  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid2175332\charrsid12147403 
Oh yes. Yes, but then of course we had our - always had our school dance, while we were at school, that was called a ball a
nd we all thought that was marvelous. Then later on of course when we got our circle of friends we would go to dances together. And - enjoy ourselves in that way.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid12589249 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid2175332\charrsid12147403 What age were you allowed to go to dances?
